article.description: — Peter Kiss scored 33 points as Bryant narrowly beat Sacred Heart 85-82 on Friday night.
article.headline: Kiss scores 33 to lift Bryant past Sacred Heart 85-82
article.linkText: Kiss scores 33 to lift Bryant past Sacred Heart 85-82
article.story: SMITHFIELD, R.I. -- — Peter Kiss scored 33 points as Bryant narrowly beat Sacred Heart 85-82 on Friday night. Charles Pride had 18 points for Bryant (6-7, 2-0 Northeast Conference). Adham Eleeda added 14 points. Aaron Clarke had 21 points for the Pioneers (5-10, 1-1). Nico Galette added 18 points and 16 rebounds, and Cantavio Dutreil had 16 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
